<fieldset class="blogblok">
<img src="/skin/unicyclist2/title-blog.cfm?Tepper" alt="Tepper" />
In unicycling I came across many people. One man who I respect enormous for teaching people positive things is Allan Tepper. When I complained that I missed him at UNICON I was told <a href="http://www.facebook.com/MrTeppersRetirement">he's about to retire</a>. And now <a href="http://www.valleyrecord.com/news/166137916.html">even the newspapers start to write about that</a>.<br />
<br />
Mr Tepper; if you read this; I only met you 3 times, but thank you so much for all you did for a lot of people. I'm sure your positive approach will be passed on by those you've teached. Your contributions will certainly be remembered! Wishing you the best!
<small>Written by <a href="http://www.unicycle.net/" title="Leo Vandewoestijne">Leo Vandewoestijne</a> on <time datetime="2012-08-14T22:32:17+00:00">Tue. the 14th of Aug 2012 at 22:32:17 GMT</time> &#160; <span class="fr"><a href="/blog/show.cfm?serial=01033" title="0 comments" onmouseover="displayStatusMsg('0 comments');return document.returnValue" onmouseout="displayStatusMsg('unicyclist.org');return document.returnValue">0 comments</a></span></small>
